ComicInfo.Title: Rigel "Where Gods May Fear to Tread!"; The Dark Horse of Death!
ComicInfo.Summary:
Rigel "Where Gods May Fear to Tread!": Thor, battling to Rigel, is diverted by the menace of Ego.
The Dark Horse of Death!: Thor and companions rest after defeating Harokin's Hordes. Harokin, mortally wounded, waits for the Black Stallion of Doom.
